'''卡拉索斯'''（[[英语|英语]]：{{lang|en|Kalathos}}）是一种形状如[[大礼帽|大礼帽]]的[[古希腊陶器|古希腊]][[花瓶|花瓶]]，用来装[[羊毛|羊毛]]与[[水果|水果]]，经常被[[古希腊|古希腊]]人当做[[生育|生育]]的象征。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/kalathos |title=Definition of Kalathos |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060333/http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/kalathos |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://exhibits.museogalileo.it/vinum/object/BlackfigureKalathos.html |title=Black-figure kalathos |access-date=2013-07-20 |archive-date=2017-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201131354/https://exhibits.museogalileo.it/vinum/object/BlackfigureKalathos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>古希腊人通常也会把大小事件画在[[陶器|陶器]]上。

